text: Amnioverse is the fourth studio album by British producer and musician Lapalux. It was released on 8 November 2019 under Brainfeeder. The first single from the album, "Earth" was released on 4 October 2019. ==Critical reception== Amnioverse was met with universal acclaim reviews from critics. At Metacritic, which assigns a weighted average rating out of 100 to reviews from mainstream publications, this release received an average score of 82, based on 4 reviews ==Track listing== ==References== Category:2019 albums Category:Brainfeeder albums
